Installation:

    git clone http://github.com/sylvesterink/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlink:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    
    (If using a .gvimrc, which isn't available yet)
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Create directories for backup/temp files in home directory

    mkdir ~/.vimbackup
    mkdir ~/.vimtmp
